info.name: Mango (Medium Fat) Ice Cream
info.description:
Serves 1 | We’ve taken the king of fruits and created an ice cream flavour that rules! Our mango ice cream is made from hand-picked Alphonso mangoes sourced from Ratnagiri. This flavour is every mango lover’s fantasy come true.

Energy (Kcal) :- 149,
Carbohydrate (g):- 16,
Protein (g):- 4,
Fats (g):- 6,
Allergen Declaration:- May contain: Brazilnuts, Cashew, Hazelnuts, Pecans, Pistachio, Walnut, Peanut & Milk,
Serving size : 80 gm per person

info.name: Tender Coconut Ice Cream
info.description:
Serves 1 | An original Naturals creation, Tender Coconut ice cream is a creamy delight made with real malai from coconuts sourced from Kerala and Karnataka. Its natural, tropical sweetness makes it a must-try for every ice cream lover.

Carbohydrate (g):- 15,
Protein (g):- 4,
Fats (g):- 8,

Serving size : 80 gm per person

info.name: Thandai Ice Cream
info.description: Serves 1 | Thandai is a cold beverage often associated with the festival of Holi. We created a delicious ice cream flavour inspired by this beverage. Now celebrate Holi with even more fanfare and sweetness! You might even get into a mood to hum ‘O Rang Barse…’ as you enjoy this ice cream!
